B. YAML-first Development Plane\
\
Create YAML configuration for:\
\
1. use case definition\
2. agents\
3. workflow\
4. prompts\
5. tools\
6. policy\
7. evals\
\
The Phase 1 workflow should include:\
\
1. Intake Agent\
   - classify scenario\
   - identify firm-short case\
   - extract instruction context\
\
2. Evidence Agent\
   - call Position Tool\
   - call Settlement Tool\
   - call Reference Data Tool\
   - call Trade / Netting Tool\
\
3. Diagnosis Agent\
   - compare delivery obligation vs free inventory\
   - identify pledged / segregated / unavailable inventory\
   - check if incoming receives may cover shortfall\
   - determine reason code and recommended action\
\
4. Commentary Agent\
   - generate factual draft commentary\
   - every statement must be tied to evidence\
   - no speculation\
   - no named internal system references\
\
5. Policy / HITL Agent\
   - validate evidence grounding\
   - check no unsupported numbers or statuses\
   - check human approval is required\
   - simulate approval / rejection / needs-edit\
\
